{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_05_01",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 1話 じろじろ見ないで",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "今回オファーを受けたフェスって\n毎年夏に開催されているアイドルイベントですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So this festival we received an offer for…\nIt's an idol event held every summer‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ。ライブと一緒にアイドルが参加する企画も\n開催される。夏の人気イベントだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Along with the live performances‚ there will be special projects involving the idols.\nIt's a popular summer event.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "そのフェスにサニピと月ストが\n出演することになったんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So Sunny Peace and Moon Tempest\nare going to perform at that festival.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.7636529286,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "みんな揃って野外ステージでライブですか……\n賑やかになりそうで楽しみです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All of us will be on an outdoor stage‚ performing live…\nIt's going to be lively and exciting. I'm looking forward to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "楽しみなのはライブだけじゃないぞ\nイベントにあわせて新衣装を作ることが決まったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The excitement isn't just about the live performance.\nWe've also decided to create new outfits for the event.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば千紗が新しい衣装のデザインを\n手伝うって言ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ Chisa said she would help\nwith the design of the new outfits.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "夏のフェスにあわせた新衣装……\nやっぱり夏っぽいイメージになるのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "New outfits to match the summer festival…\nI wonder if they will have a summer-like image.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "もしデザインで要望があれば遠慮なく言ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you have any requests regarding the design‚ don't hesitate to let us know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね……しいて言うなら動きやすさでしょうか\n他に要望は特にありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… if I had to say‚ it would be about ease of movement.\nOther than that‚ I don't have any specific requests.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "千紗のセンスを信頼していますから\nどんなデザインの衣装でも着こなしてみせます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I trust Chisa's sense of style‚\nso I'll be able to pull off any design of outfit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "頼もしいな\nじゃあデザインは俺達に全部任せてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's reassuring.\nWell then‚ leave the design to us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "はい。夏のビーチに似合う衣装、楽しみにしてますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright. I'm looking forward to the outfits that will be perfect for the summer beach.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数週間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― After few weeks",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.8
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……と言う訳で、衣装のサンプルが出来上がったから\n試着してほしいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So‚ the samples for the outfits are ready‚\nand I want you to try it on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "実際に着てみて気付いたことがあれば\nなんでも気兼ねなく言ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you notice anything while actually wearing it‚\nfeel free to let me know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "それは分かりましたけど……\nここにあるのが、その新衣装なんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand‚ but…\nare these the new outfits here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうだが……どうかしたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right‚ but… is something wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "どうかしたのかじゃありません\nこれ、ほとんど水着じゃないですか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not about something being wrong.\nThese are practically swimsuits‚ aren't they?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "生地が薄いし、布面積も少な過ぎます\nこんなに肌の露出が多いなんて聞いてません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The fabric is thin‚ and there's very little coverage.\nI didn't hear anything about so much skin exposure.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そうか？　夏のビーチに似合うというコンセプトなら\n水着風の衣装は順当だと思うが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so? If the concept is to match a summer beach…\nI think a swimsuit-like outfit is appropriate.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "順当って……{user}さんは他人事だから\nそんな風に言えるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Appropriate… It's easy for {user} to say that\nbecause it doesn't concern you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.8172012329,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "もっと自分の身になって……\n自分がこれを着た姿を想像してみて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Try to think in my position.\nCan you imagine yourself wearing this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "うっ……想像しちゃったじゃないですか！\nなんて物を想像させるんですか！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… You made me imagine it!\nWhy are you making me imagine such things!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "勝手に想像して怒られてもな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why do you get angry from imagining it on your own…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "あ……そ、そうですね、すみません……\n予想外のデザインだったので少し取り乱しました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… R-Right‚ I'm sorry…\nIt was an unexpected design‚ so I got a little flustered.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "とりあえず一度着てみないか？\n実際に着てみたら印象が変わるかもしれないだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For now‚ why don't you try it on?\nThe impression might change once you actually wear it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 158
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "……分かりました。着替えるので\n{user}さんは外で待っていて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Understood. I'll change.\n{user}‚ please wait outside.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
